Osborne Says Euro Region Needs to Deal With Debt, Weak Banks

-- B y   G o n z a l o   V i n a
-- 
2011-10-03T07:28:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/osborne-says-euro-region-needs-to-deal-with-debt-weak-banks.html
U.K. Chancellor of the Exchequer
 George Osborne  repeated calls for euro-area countries to bolster
banks and increase the “firepower” of their bailout fund in
order to prevent further damage to the British economy.  “They need to make a decision, make it now and stick to
it,” Osborne told BBC Radio 4 today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
